'''韋德·麥克勞克倫''' {{post-nominals|country=CAN|CM|OPEI}}（{{lang|en|Wade MacLauchlan}}，{{bd|1954年|12月10日||}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]政治人物，2015年-19年間為第32任[[愛德華王子島省省長|愛德華王子島省省長]]、[[愛德華王子島省議會|愛德華王子島省議會]]約克－牡蠣床選區議員和愛德華王子島自由黨黨魁<ref name=globe>{{cite news|title=PEI Liberals rally behind outsider Wade MacLauchlan to lead party|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/pei-liberals-rally-behind-outsider-wade-maclauchlan-to-lead-party/article22234747/|accessdate=December 30, 2014|work=Globe and Mail|date=December 29, 2014|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108125143/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/pei-liberals-rally-behind-outsider-wade-maclauchlan-to-lead-party/article22234747/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=At 60, Wade MacLauchlan making leap into politics as P.E.I. premier|url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/at-60-wade-maclauchlan-making-leap-into-politics-as-p-e-i-premier-1.2246886|accessdate=February 23, 2015|work=CTV News|date=February 21, 2015|archive-date=2018-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815164230/https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/at-60-wade-maclauchlan-making-leap-into-politics-as-p-e-i-premier-1.2246886|dead-url=no}}</ref>，為該省首位公開同性戀身份的省長<ref name="CE"/>及全加拿大首位公開男同性戀身份的省長<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|last=Wherry|first=Aaron|date=February 25, 2015|title=Prince Edward Island wins a premier with ambition and experience to spare|url=https://www.macleans.ca/news/canada/pei-premier/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831210208/https://www.macleans.ca/news/canada/pei-premier/|archive-date=2018-08-31|access-date=2020-09-07|website=Maclean's|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在此之前他曾於1999年-2011年間出任[[愛德華王子島大學|愛德華王子島大學]]校長，2012年成為該校榮休校長。

==早年生活==
麥克勞克倫在[[愛德華王子島|愛德華王子島]]斯坦霍普（{{lang|en|Stanhope}}）出生，家裏五名子女中排行第三，父母在當地營商<ref>{{Cite web|last=Mackay|first=Mary|date=|title=Here's to Dad|url=https://www.theguardian.pe.ca/lifestyles/heres-to-dad-108577/|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-09-06|website=www.theguardian.pe.ca}}</ref><ref name="CE">{{Cite web |first=Katrine |last=Raymond |date=2019-04-24 |title=Wade MacLauchlan |url=https://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/wade-maclauchlan |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126225507/https://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.ca/en/article/wade-maclauchlan |archive-date=2021-01-26 |access-date=2020-11-02 |publisher=The Canadian Encyclopedia |dead-url=no }}</ref>。韋德從斯坦霍普學校畢業後到[[夏洛特敦|夏洛特敦]]郊區中學就讀，曾任學生會副主席，並獲教師提名於1970年-71年間在[[愛德華王子島省議會|愛德華王子島省議會]]出任侍員<ref name="CE"/>。他於1976年從[[愛德華王子島大學|愛德華王子島大學]]獲取工商管理學士學位<ref>{{Cite web|date=2003|title=President's Message |url=http://welcome.upei.ca/Winter2003Magazine.pdf |archive-url= |archive-date= |access-date=2020-11-02 |publisher=''UPEI Magazine''}}</ref>，1981年從[[新不倫瑞克大學|新布藍茲維大學]]法學院取得[[法學士|法學士]]學位<ref name="UNB">{{Cite web |date=2018-04-23 |title=UNB celebrates 125th anniversary of Faculty of Law with successful gala dinner |url=https://blogs.unb.ca/newsroom/2018/04/unb-celebrates-125th-anniversary-of-faculty-of-law-with-successful-gala-dinner.php |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210526050426/https://blogs.unb.ca/newsroom/2018/04/unb-celebrates-125th-anniversary-of-faculty-of-law-with-successful-gala-dinner.php |archive-date=2021-05-26 |access-date=2020-11-02 |publisher=[[新不倫瑞克大學|新布藍茲維大學]] |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後於[[加拿大最高法院|加拿大最高法院]]任職法律文員至1982年，再於1983年從[[耶魯大學|耶魯大學]]取得[[法學碩士|法學碩士]]學位<ref name="CE"/>。

==學術事業==
麥克勞克倫於1983年加入[[諾華士高沙|諾華斯高沙省]][[戴爾豪斯大學|戴爾豪斯大學]]法學院<ref name="CE"/>，先後任職助理教授和副教授至1991年。他於1991年返回母校[[新不倫瑞克大學|新布藍茲維大學]]出任法學院院長至1996年，1997年-99年間則任該校物業研究中心總監<ref name="CE"/><ref name="UNB"/>。此外，他亦曾於1989年-90年間出任[[蒙特婁|蒙特婁]][[麥基爾大學|麥基爾大學]]客席教授，並曾分別於[[瑞士|瑞士]][[洛桑大學|洛桑大學]]和[[澳洲|澳洲]][[墨爾本大學|墨爾本大學]]出任客席研究員<ref name="CE"/>。

他於1999年返回另一母校[[愛德華王子島大學|愛德華王子島大學]]，出任該校第五任校長<ref name="CE"/><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=Summer 1999|title=Celebrating a coming of age |url=http://vre2.upei.ca/upeimag/fedora/repository/upeimag:199909-au/-/UPEI%20Magazine%20-%20Summer%201999|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=|publisher=''UPEI Magazine''}}</ref>。在該省以至整個[[加拿大大西洋省份|加拿大大西洋地區]]面臨青年人口下降的背景下，麥克勞克倫以提升該校招生人數為首要任務。在他領導下，該校全讀生數目從1999年的2450人上升至2001-02學年的逾2850人<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=October 15, 2001|title=Association of Atlantic Universities, 2001-2002 Preliminary Survey of Enrolments|url=https://www.atlanticuniversities.ca/sites/default/files/documents/AAUFactsFiguresEnrolments/fulltime.0102.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220124175043/https://www.atlanticuniversities.ca/sites/default/files/documents/AAUFactsFiguresEnrolments/fulltime.0102.pdf|archive-date=2022-01-24|access-date=|website=|dead-url=no}}</ref>，再於2010-11學年達致近4000人<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=October 14, 2010|title=ASSOCIATION OF ATLANTIC UNIVERSITIES 2010-2011 PRELIMINARY SURVEY OF ENROLMENTS|url=https://www.atlanticuniversities.ca/sites/default/files/documents/AAUFactsFiguresEnrolments/PreliminaryEnrolments%20Full%20Time%2010-11.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220124160930/https://www.atlanticuniversities.ca/sites/default/files/documents/AAUFactsFiguresEnrolments/PreliminaryEnrolments%20Full%20Time%2010-11.pdf|archive-date=2022-01-24|access-date=|website=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。期間該校在《[[麥克林|麥克林]]》雜誌的大學排名榜地位亦有所改進，在21間主要為本科大學的排名中從2000年的第18名上升至2006年的第5名<ref>{{Cite web|last=DWYER|first=MARY|title=OUR 16TH ANNUAL RANKINGS {{!}} Maclean's {{!}} NOV. 13th 2006|url=https://archive.macleans.ca/article/2006/11/13/our-16th-annual-rankings|access-date=2020-09-05|website=Maclean's {{!}} The Complete Archive|language=en-CA|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127145250/https://archive.macleans.ca/article/2006/11/13/our-16th-annual-rankings|dead-url=no}}</ref>。麥克勞克倫就任後亦定下目標，倍增該校的科研和發展資金<ref name=":0" />；該校的外部研究資金從1999年的每年200萬元上升至2002年的520萬元，總研究資金再於2007年達致1320萬元<ref>Research Infosource, ''Canada's Innovation Leaders 2008''</ref>。他任内亦見證該校多項擴張項目得以落實，包括新建的學生中心、商學院和加拿大國家研究委員會設施<ref name="CE"/>。

他的校長任期於2011年末屆滿，2012年獲名為該校榮休校長。他於2009年成為Medavie健康基金會的董事會成員，並於2013年成為董事會主席；該會為協助青少年應對精神健康和二型糖尿病的項目提供資金<ref name="CE"/>。

==從政==
麥克勞克倫於2012年11月當選愛德華王子島北岸自治區議員，首度出任民選公職<ref name="CE"/>，並於2014年11月在無競爭對手下自動連任。他並從2013年-15年間出任愛德華王子島城鎮聯會的董事會成員<ref name="CE"/>。

2014年11月13日，[[愛德華王子島省省長|愛德華王子島省省長]]和愛德華王子島自由黨黨魁吉茲（{{lang|en|Robert Ghiz}}）突然宣布辭職；兩周後麥克勞克倫宣布競逐該黨黨魁職務<ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|date=November 28, 2014|title=Wade MacLauchlan announces P.E.I. Liberal leadership bid|work=CBC News|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/prince-edward-island/wade-maclauchlan-announces-p-e-i-liberal-leadership-bid-1.2853405|access-date=|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402014858/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/prince-edward-island/wade-maclauchlan-announces-p-e-i-liberal-leadership-bid-1.2853405|dead-url=no}}</ref>。提名期於2015年1月20日結束後尚未有其他候選人參選，麥克勞克倫遂於同年2月21日自動當選自由黨黨魁<ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|date=February 21, 2015|title=Wade MacLauchlan confirmed as P.E.I. Liberal leader|work=CBC News|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/prince-edward-island/wade-maclauchlan-confirmed-as-p-e-i-liberal-leader-1.2966188|access-date=|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115011024/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/prince-edward-island/wade-maclauchlan-confirmed-as-p-e-i-liberal-leader-1.2966188|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於同月23日宣誓就任第32任愛德華王子島省省長，同時兼任該省財政及能源廳長、和跨政府事務、原住民事務和法語系居民事務廳長<ref>{{Cite web|date=2015-02-23|title=Wade MacLauchlan takes over as P.E.I. premier, replacing Robert Ghiz|url=https://atlantic.ctvnews.ca/wade-maclauchlan-takes-over-as-p-e-i-premier-replacing-robert-ghiz-1.2248785?cache=yesclipId104062%3FclipId%3D64268|access-date=2020-09-06|website=Atlantic|language=en}}</ref>。

[[File:Wade_MacLauchlan_-_2015_Election.png|thumb]]
2015年5月4日省選，麥克勞克倫帶領自由黨贏取[[愛德華王子島省議會|省議會]]27個議席中的18個，以多數姿態繼續執政。他本人則在約克－牡蠣床選區（{{lang|en|York-Oyster Bed}}）當選省議員，首度晉身省議會<ref>{{Cite web|last=Bissett|first=Kevin|date=2015-05-04|title=Liberals win P.E.I. election, but Tories gain and Greens make history|url=https://atlantic.ctvnews.ca/liberals-win-p-e-i-election-but-tories-gain-and-greens-make-history-1.2357211|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181104071225/https://atlantic.ctvnews.ca/liberals-win-p-e-i-election-but-tories-gain-and-greens-make-history-1.2357211|archive-date=2018-11-04|access-date=2020-09-06|website=CTV Atlantic|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在新一屆省議會除了出任省長外，亦兼任司法廳長。

麥克勞克倫任職省長期間著重擴闊該省經濟和振興該省人口。愛德華王子島從2015年-19年間的省民生產總值累計上升16%<ref>Statistics Canada.  Table  36-10-0402-02   Gross domestic product (GDP) at basic prices, by industry, provinces and territories, growth rates (x 1,000,000)</ref>，增幅為全國眾省之最，並遠高於同期加拿大國民生產總值所增長的9%。此外該省從2015年5月到2019年12月的全職工作職位總數亦上升8500份，相當於當地勞工市場的14.2%<ref>Statistics Canada, ''Labour Force Survey'', Characteristics by Province, December 2019, FT employment PEI 68,200 <nowiki>https://www150.statcan.gc.ca/n1/daily-quotidien/200110/t003a-eng.htm</nowiki>. ''Labour Force Survey,'' Characteristics by Province, May 2015, FT employment PEI 59,700 <nowiki>https://www150.statcan.gc.ca/n1/daily-quotidien/150605/t150605a003-eng.htm</nowiki></ref>；增幅主要來自私人企業，覆蓋製造業、建築業、農業、漁業、旅遊業、運輸業和批發貿易等行業<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2018-05-02|title=Gross Domestic Product (GDP) by Industry|url=https://www.princeedwardisland.ca/en/information/finance/gross-domestic-product-gdp-industry|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124151808/https://www.princeedwardisland.ca/en/information/finance/gross-domestic-product-gdp-industry|archive-date=2021-01-24|access-date=2020-09-06|website=www.princeedwardisland.ca|dead-url=no}}</ref>。受惠於良好經濟因素，該省人口亦從2015年的14萬4546人上升9%至2019年的15萬6947，這些年間為全國人口及移民增長速度最快的省份<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2019|title=PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND POPULATION REPORT|url=https://www.princeedwardisland.ca/sites/default/files/publications/pt_pop_rep_0.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310002555/https://www.princeedwardisland.ca/sites/default/files/publications/pt_pop_rep_0.pdf|archive-date=2021-03-10|access-date=|website=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該省的居民年齡中位數亦從2016年的44歲下降至2019年的43.2歲，為1968年以來首次出現下降趨勢<ref>Statistics Canada.  Table  17-10-0005-01   Population estimates on July 1st, by age and sex</ref>。

麥克勞克倫亦主張平衡預算；該省於2015-16財政年度錄得1300萬元赤字，2017-18年度則錄得7500萬元盈餘，2018-19年度再錄得5700萬元盈餘<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2019-10-31|title=Public Accounts Volume I 2019|url=https://www.princeedwardisland.ca/en/publication/public-accounts-volume-i-2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125105358/https://www.princeedwardisland.ca/en/publication/public-accounts-volume-i-2019|archive-date=2021-01-25|access-date=2020-09-06|website=www.princeedwardisland.ca|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該省的負債對省民生產總值比率從2015年的36.7%下降至2019年的30.5%，為加拿大東部眾省最低，其[[DBRS|DBRS]]信貸評級亦於2019年8月上調至A級<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=August 19, 2019|title=P.E.I. credit rating increased to A for the first time since 2000|url=https://www.theguardian.pe.ca/news/local/pei-bond-rating-upgraded-to-a-for-first-time-since-2000-342872/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822213200/https://www.theguardian.pe.ca/news/local/pei-bond-rating-upgraded-to-a-for-first-time-since-2000-342872/|archive-date=2019-08-22|access-date=2020-09-06|website=www.theguardian.pe.ca|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

執政接近12年的自由黨於2019年省選中失利，只贏取省議會6個議席<ref>{{Cite web|title=2019 Election Results {{!}} Elections PEI|url=https://www.electionspei.ca/2019-election-results|access-date=2020-09-07|website=www.electionspei.ca|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423122038/https://www.electionspei.ca/2019-election-results|dead-url=no}}</ref>。麥克勞克倫則在斯坦霍普－馬什菲爾德選區（{{lang|en|Stanhope-Marshfield}}）以104票之差敗予進步保守黨候選人<ref>{{Cite web|title=District 8 Results: Stanhope-Marshfield {{!}} Elections PEI|url=https://www.electionspei.ca/district-8-results-stanhope-marshfield|access-date=2020-09-07|website=www.electionspei.ca|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228003154/https://www.electionspei.ca/district-8-results-stanhope-marshfield|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於選後兩日宣布辭任自由黨黨魁<ref>{{Cite web|title=Wade MacLauchlan to step down as P.E.I. Liberal leader after third-place finish|url=https://globalnews.ca/news/5207774/wade-maclauchlan-to-step-down/|access-date=2020-09-06|website=Global News|language=en-CA|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103122501/https://globalnews.ca/news/5207774/wade-maclauchlan-to-step-down/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

